      p.about__p
        span.about__person.about__person--michail Michail
        | We were already super adorable at that point, so we watched the Lion King and ate a frozen pizza while holding hands on Sarah‚Äôs couch. Today, we consider that to be our first date, and we celebrate our anniversary on that day ‚Äî September 18, 2008.
      p.about__p
