        |  Yep! Throw in a few more years of high school, 2 ¬Ω years of long distance during college, a couple years together in Ohio, a few years in San Francisco, and that basically brings us up to today! We just moved to Seattle in May, and we‚Äôve got some longer term travel intentions as well.
